true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e无论怎么样，就冲你这份对数学的勇气就为你点赞  \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561425017,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"24b90b8f3118bf59d31ec14b665155cd","url_token":"xie-xue-43-19","name":"梧桐是妖怪吧","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-5178e4922ac66a3d3c435f276b47b1fa_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-5178e4922ac66a3d3c435f276b47b1fa_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/24b90b8f3118bf59d31ec14b665155cd","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561425017","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545966650,"updated_time":1545968206,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e回答个无关的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e知乎的风气真的挺油腻又恶臭的…放眼望去都是冷嘲热讽 如果不是营销号 就算最后是闹剧 别人高中年轻气盛的大喊证明哥猜知乎的风气真的挺油腻又恶臭的…放眼望去都是冷嘲热讽 如果不是营销号 就算最后是闹剧 别人高中年轻气盛的大喊证明了哥猜 也不至于如此冷嘲热讽 一群说不定数学从来没及格过的人 这儿叭叭叭啥呢\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560488263,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"048d91e7b2800d5ab5e39556064934d7","url_token":"xiao-jing-98-99","name":"小京","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/048d91e7b2800d5ab5e39556064934d7","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560488263","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-58d6ead135faa13688bb01d1ab6d5129_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545842081,"updated_time":1545842092,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e来自于空间\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我大致观看了一下各位大佬的评论 也去百度了一下哥德巴赫猜想究竟是什么 我看不懂 或许能有比我看懂的人在 但我无法否定他们究竟是否是真的懂 因为我并不懂 正如一位大佬所说的那样 井蛙不可语海 夏虫不可语冰 朝菌不知晦朔 蟪蛄不知春秋 在座的各位不也都如井蛙和夏虫一般?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于我们所不了解的事情妄加评论 这好像的确是种不厚道的事情 或许你可能觉得他不够格才一个高中生 可是究竟是怎样的人才是够格的呢?民科?世界著名数学家?大家每一个人都是人 为何不能有权力去证明呢?如果如果一个高中生有这种兴趣想去证明哥德巴赫猜想 那我们为什么要去打消他这种念头并去嘲笑呢?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e反正就一句话 如果证明出来了我们该欣喜该鼓舞该欢呼 如果证明不出来也不用去打击(那科学家们证明不出来怎么没见你去打击呢)尽量的鼓励吧 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e完\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1fa5c73d96676a693240de2af136b696_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"407\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0e8ca176682db53178ff51723454b7d7_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1fa5c73d96676a693240de2af136b696_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='640'%20height='407'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"407\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0e8ca176682db53178ff51723454b7d7_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1fa5c73d96676a693240de2af136b696_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1fa5c73d96676a693240de2af136b696_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003